883
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:50,840
full of marshes,

884
00:41:51,120 --> 00:41:52,040
very hard to travel.

885
00:41:52,680 --> 00:41:54,480
That doesn't mean impossible.

886
00:41:54,800 --> 00:41:56,240
If the road has been mapped out,

887
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:57,840
