902
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,720
You really are an expert.

903
00:42:29,720 --> 00:42:30,840
You know everything.

904
00:42:31,520 --> 00:42:33,280
Now help me figure out a way,

905
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:34,000
expert,

